text:
Hey folks, I'm looking for guidance. What are some of the best platforms to charge recurring revenue from international clients? I run a slack community + want to make it a paid community.

The platform should have:
• Lesser fee
• Payment link option
• Coupon Code system
Please don't say PayPal, they take kidneys as fees.

I've tried Razorpay but it is only allowing me to receive money in INR. I've tried Zoho payments app but it integrates with Razorpay gateway. Same case with Buymeacoffee.

elements.text:

I've tried Razorpay but it is only allowing me to receive money in INR. I've tried Zoho payments app but it integrates with Razorpay gateway. Same case with Buymeacoffee.
